The,Semantics,Push,API,allows,developers,to,integrate,price,change,notifications,into,their,websites,and,applications,Users,can,submit,a,product,or,URL,that,they,want,to,track,and,receive,notifications,when,the,price,increases,or,decreases,This,API,is,provided,by,Semantics,a,company,that,offers,product,and,pricing,APIs,for,e,commerce,applications